# Active Directory Home Lab

## Objective
Build a secure enterprise-like Windows Active Directory environment using VMware to simulate a corporate network.

## Environment
VMware Workstation
Windows Server 2022
Windows 10 Client
Virtual Network

## Skills Practiced
Active Directory Domain Services
Domain Controller Configuration
User and Group Management
Group Policy Configuration
Network Segmentation
Authentication and Authorization

## Security Focus
Configured domain authentication
Applied least privilege principles
Simulated attack scenarios and analyzed logs

## Outcome
Successfully built a functioning Active Directory domain environment with domain-joined workstations and centralized authentication.

## Tools Used
VMware
Windows Server
Active Directory
PowerShell
